《萬聖節大作戰》主要獲得正面的評價。評論家主要讚揚其獨特性和魅力，但就批評其陳舊的遊戲機制。1up給予此遊戲A-等級，指稱讚其樸實的遊戲模式和引人注目的設計，但就批評其鏡頭問題。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.1up.com/reviews/costume-quest-review|title=Costume Quest Review (PS3, XBOX 360, PC)|author=Alice Liang|publisher=1up|date=2010-10-20|accessdate=2013-05-22|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130312150846/http://www.1up.com/reviews/costume-quest-review|archivedate=2013-03-12}}</ref>[[GameRankings|GameRankings]]分別給予此遊戲的Xbox 360版本和PlayStation 3版本79%和77.78%的分數。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamerankings.com/xbox360/604987-costume-quest/index.html|title=Costume Quest|publisher=GameRankings|accessdate=2013-05-22|archive-date=2019-12-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191209012850/https://www.gamerankings.com/xbox360/604987-costume-quest/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]則分別給予此遊戲的Xbox 360版本和PlayStation 3版本74/100<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/game/playstation-3/costume-quest|title=Costume Quest PlayStation 3|publisher=Metacritic|accessdate=2013-05-22|archive-date=2021-02-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210227193827/https://www.metacritic.com/game/playstation-3/costume-quest|dead-url=no}}</ref>和77/100<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/game/xbox-360/costume-quest|title=Costume Quest Xbox 360|publisher=Metacritic|accessdate=2013-05-22|archive-date=2021-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225225851/http://www.metacritic.com/game/xbox-360/costume-quest|dead-url=no}}</ref>的分數。[[Game_Informer|Game Informer]]給予此遊戲6/10分，並指出此遊戲過程無聊，根本不適合任何年齡階層的玩家。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.gameinformer.com/games/costume_quest/b/xbox360/archive/2010/10/20/costume-quest-review-too-much-trick-not-enough-treat.aspx|title=Costume Quest Review: Too Much Trick, Not Enough Treat|publisher=Game Informer|date=2010-10-20|author=Joe Juba|accessdate=2013-05-22|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126025618/https://www.gameinformer.com/games/costume_quest/b/xbox360/archive/2010/10/20/costume-quest-review-too-much-trick-not-enough-treat.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]給予此遊戲7/10分，讚揚其視覺設計、幽默和服裝系統，但就批評其戰鬥系統和展出問題。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://asia.gamespot.com/costume-quest/reviews/costume-quest-review-6282502/|title=Costume Quest Review|publisher=GameSpot|date=2010-10-20|author=Giancarlo Varanini|accessdate=2013-05-22|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121126011810/http://asia.gamespot.com/costume-quest/reviews/costume-quest-review-6282502/|archivedate=2012-11-26}}</ref>[[IGN|IGN]]則給予此遊戲7.5/10分，盛讚其設計和音樂，但就認為遊戲過程仍須改善。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2010/10/21/costume-quest-review-2|title=Costume Quest Review Is this Halloween-themed RPG a trick or a treat?|author=Kristine Steimer|publisher=IGN|date=2010-10-20|accessdate=2013-05-22|archive-date=2017-05-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170520153605/http://www.ign.com/articles/2010/10/21/costume-quest-review-2|dead-url=no}}</ref>

